    <section class="about-section container" id="about">
      <div class="about-panel">
        <div class="about-meta">
          <p class="kicker">About the Creator</p>
          <h2>Meet the young developer behind Hudā</h2>
          <div class="about-name">
            <div>
              <div class="about-title">Moustapha Gueye</div>
              <div class="about-role">Founder &amp; Developer</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-body">
          <p><strong>As-salāmu ʿalaykum wa raḥmatullāh,</strong></p>
          <p>My name is Moustapha, and I am the creator of Hudā. I am 18 years old at the time of release, and I have been Muslim my entire life, alhamdulillāh. Although I was born into Islam, I understand that many people come to Islam later in life, and I have immense respect for those who find their way to the truth.</p>
          <p>This app was developed entirely by me. Every part of it — the design, the code, the content — was created with care, intention, and the hope that it could make a difference in someone's life.</p>
          <p>Hudā is not just an app; it's a project of the heart. It's my way of giving back and using the skills that Allah has blessed me with to benefit others, in shā' Allāh. I am still learning and growing, and I hope this app reflects that journey.</p>
          <p><em>May Allah guide us all, increase us in knowledge, and make this effort a source of reward.</em></p>
          <p>Thank you for being here. I truly wish you the best in your journey.</p>
          <p class="about-signoff">Was-salāmu ʿalaykum wa raḥmatullāhi wa barakātuh.</p>
          <p class="about-signoff about-signature">– Moustapha Gueye, Founder</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

